    public class TestFederatedQuery<S extends IIndexManager>
extends AbstractTestNanoSparqlClient<S>
    Proxied test suite for SPARQL 1.1 Federated Query. In general, each test loads some data into the KB and then issues a federated query. The core tests are W3C tests and have the pattern serviceXX. There are also tests developed for openrdf.
    See Also:
    W3C Tests , Federated Query Test Suite
